                </p>

                <ul class="list-disc px-4 ml-4 text-sm mb-4">
                    <li><strong>Legal Protection of Personal Assets:</strong> With a registered company, your personal money and property are kept out of your business so your savings and property will not be exposed to any business debts or legal problems.</li>
                    <li><strong>The Tax Benefits and Tax Compliance:</strong> Selecting an appropriate structure can allow your startup to enjoy tax deductions and tax credits without any issue in remaining fully compliant with the law.</li>
